The '''80th UAV Squadron''' ({{lang-nl|80 UAV Eskadron}}) is a [[Squadron (aviation)|squadron]] in the [[Belgian Air Force|Air Component]] of the [[Military of Belgium|Belgian Armed Forces]]. It is dedicated to [[unmanned aerial vehicle]]s or UAVs. It is organised like a [[Wing (air force unit)|wing]] and consists of a Flight Group, a Maintenance Group and a Support Group.

