In [[Wendish mythology]] '''Misizla''' (or '''Sicksa''') was a [[god]]like [[hero]]. He was a warrior-musician wearing sword and armour, playing his bagpipe. He may in fact be [[Misizlaw]] (died 999) who wanted to restore Slavic pagan faith.

