The '''[[Diocese]] of [[Bovino]]''' was a [[Roman Catholic]] diocese in [[Apulia]], southern [[Italy]],<ref name=CathHierBovino>[http://www.catholic-hierarchy.org/diocese/db241.html "Diocese of Bovino"] ''[[Catholic-Hierarchy.org]]''. David M. Cheney. Retrieved March 21, 2016</ref><ref name=GCathBovino>[http://www.gcatholic.org/dioceses/former/bovi0.htm "Diocese of Bovino"] ''GCatholic.org''. Gabriel Chow. Retrieved February 29, 2016</ref> established in the fifth century.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.newadvent.org/cathen/02724b.htm|title=Bovino|work=[[Catholic Encyclopedia]] |accessdate=2007-02-18}}</ref> In 1986 it was merged into the [[Archdiocese of Foggia-Bovino]].
